speech.speakeroffice: The Minister for Small Business, Industry and Enterprise
speech.p: Will the hon. Lady agree to meet me, in confidence, in relation to all these people? As the Minister responsible for retail, I undertake to take this up directly with B&Q. May I ask that she also speaks to the right hon. Member for Doncaster North (Edward Miliband) about this, because I think that between us we could do something about it?
